rk data.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.uberlink.com/software#voson-nodexl\">VOSON Data Provider for NodeXL</a> (<a href=\"https://blogs.k-state.edu/it-news/2013/04/09/the-nodexl-series-using-voson-for-hyperlink-network-analysis-part-9/\">quick tutorial</a>; to be discontinued in 2016).</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://vosonlab.net/tools\">vosonR</a> - R client for the VOSON software (in development).</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2016-04-23T21:17:21.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"briatte/awesome-network-analysis","categoryHTML":"<h2>Professional Groups</h2><h3>Research Groups (Other)</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://vosonlab.net/\">Virtual Observatory for the Study of Online Networks (VOSON)</a> - Research and software development project located at the Australian National University.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-04-23T21:10:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"cyclejs-community/awesome-cyclejs","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Example Applications</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/grozen/trends-cycle\">grozen/trends-cycle ★3</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/grozen/trends-cycle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":3,\"repo\":\"grozen/trends-cycle\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Slack trend searching written in Cycle.js</li>","updatedAt":"2016-04-23T18:57:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"cyclejs-community/awesome-cyclejs","categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Utilities</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://gith